(154, '674', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0330373', 'Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire', 2005, 'images/674 poster.jpg', 7.4, 'images/674 cover.jpg', 'Harry starts his fourth year at Hogwarts, competes in the treacherous Triwizard Tournament and faces the evil Lord Voldemort. Ron and Hermione help Harry manage the pressure â€“ but Voldemort lurks, awaiting his chance to destroy Harry and all that he stands for.', 'en', '2005-11-05', 'Mike Newell', 'Patalex IV Productions Limited', '157 minutes', '150000000', '895921036', 7, ' ', 'Dark And Difficult Times Lie Ahead.', '2005-11-05 00:00:00'),
(155, '155', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0468569', 'The Dark Knight', 2008, 'images/155 poster.jpg', 8.2, 'images/155 cover.jpg', 'Batman raises the stakes in his war on crime. With the help of Lt. Jim Gordon and District Attorney Harvey Dent, Batman sets out to dismantle the remaining criminal organizations that plague the streets. The partnership proves to be effective, but they soon find themselves prey to a reign of chaos unleashed by a rising criminal mastermind known to the terrified citizens of Gotham as the Joker.', 'en', '2008-07-16', 'Christopher Nolan', 'DC Comics', '152 minutes', '185000000', '1004558444', 9, '      Christian Bale and Heath Ledger deadly combination. Heath Ledger''s last movie.', 'Why So Serious?', '2008-07-16 00:00:00'),
(156, '49026', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1345836', 'The Dark Knight Rises', 2012, 'images/49026 poster.jpg', 7.5, 'images/49026 cover.jpg', 'Following the death of District Attorney Harvey Dent, Batman assumes responsibility for Dent''s crimes to protect the late attorney''s reputation and is subsequently hunted by the Gotham City Police Department. Eight years later, Batman encounters the mysterious Selina Kyle and the villainous Bane, a new terrorist leader who overwhelms Gotham''s finest. The Dark Knight resurfaces to protect a city that has branded him an enemy.', 'en', '2012-07-16', 'Christopher Nolan', 'Legendary Pictures', '165 minutes', '250000000', '1084939099', 10, '  Everything in this movie is just perfect. Loved Christian Bale...', 'The Legend Ends', '2012-07-16 00:00:00'),
(157, '272', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0372784', 'Batman Begins', 2005, 'images/272 poster.jpg', 7.5, 'images/272 cover.jpg', 'Driven by tragedy, billionaire Bruce Wayne dedicates his life to uncovering and defeating the corruption that plagues his home, Gotham City.  Unable to work within the system, he instead creates a new identity, a symbol of fear for the criminal underworld - The Batman.', 'en', '2005-06-10', 'Christopher Nolan', 'DC Comics', '140 minutes', '150000000', '374218673', 9, ' The beginning of the best Batman (by far) series  ...', 'Evil fears the knight.', '2005-06-10 00:00:00'),
(158, '550', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0137523', 'Fight Club', 1999, 'images/550 poster.jpg', 8.2, 'images/550 cover.jpg', 'A ticking-time-bomb insomniac and a slippery soap salesman channel primal male aggression into a shocking new form of therapy. Their concept catches on, with underground ', 'en', '1999-10-15', 'David Fincher', 'Regency Enterprises', '139 minutes', '63000000', '100853753', 7, '', 'Mischief. Mayhem. Soap.', '2017-07-01 03:32:21'),
(159, '278', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0111161', 'The Shawshank Redemption', 1994, 'images/278 poster.jpg', 8.5, 'images/278 cover.jpg', 'Framed in the 1940s for the double murder of his wife and her lover, upstanding banker Andy Dufresne begins a new life at the Shawshank prison, where he puts his accounting skills to work for an amoral warden. During his long stretch in prison, Dufresne comes to be admired by the other inmates -- including an older prisoner named Red -- for his integrity and unquenchable sense of hope.', 'en', '1994-09-23', 'Frank Darabont', 'Castle Rock Entertainment', '142 minutes', '25000000', '28341469', 6, ' Not for me ..IMDB no. 1 movie ...', 'Fear can hold you prisoner. Hope can set you free.', '2017-07-01 03:32:55'),
(160, '603', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0133093', 'The Matrix', 1999, 'images/603 poster.jpg', 7.9, 'images/603 cover.jpg', 'Set in the 22nd century, The Matrix tells the story of a computer hacker who joins a group of underground insurgents fighting the vast and powerful computers who now rule the earth.', 'en', '1999-03-30', 'Lilly Wachowski', 'Village Roadshow Pictures', '136 minutes', '63000000', '463517383', 9, '', 'Welcome to the Real World.', '2017-07-01 03:34:03'),
(161, '604', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0234215', 'The Matrix Reloaded', 2003, 'images/604 poster.jpg', 6.7, 'images/604 cover.jpg', 'Six months after the events depicted in The Matrix, Neo has proved to be a good omen for the free humans, as more and more humans are being freed from the matrix and brought to Zion, the one and only stronghold of the Resistance.  Neo himself has discovered his superpowers including super speed, ability to see the codes of the things inside the matrix and a certain degree of pre-cognition. But a nasty piece of news hits the human resistance: 250,000 machine sentinels are digging to Zion and would reach them in 72 hours. As Zion prepares for the ultimate war, Neo, Morpheus and Trinity are advised by the Oracle to find the Keymaker who would help them reach the Source.  Meanwhile Neo''s recurrent dreams depicting Trinity''s death have got him worried and as if it was not enough, Agent Smith has somehow escaped deletion, has become more powerful than before and has fixed Neo as his next target.', 'en', '2003-05-15', 'Lilly Wachowski', 'Village Roadshow Pictures', '138 minutes', '150000000', '738599701', 9, ' ', 'Free your mind.', '2003-05-15 00:00:00'),
(162, '605', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0242653', 'The Matrix Revolutions', 2003, 'images/605 poster.jpg', 6.4, 'images/605 cover.jpg', 'The human city of Zion defends itself against the massive invasion of the machines as Neo fights to end the war at another front while also opposing the rogue Agent Smith.', 'en', '2003-11-05', 'Lilly Wachowski', 'Village Roadshow Pictures', '129 minutes', '150000000', '424988211', 7, 'The ending was confusing .......', 'Everything that has a beginning has an end.', '2017-07-01 03:35:22'),
(163, '597', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120338', 'Titanic', 1997, 'images/597 poster.jpg', 7.4, 'images/597 cover.jpg', '84 years later, a 101-year-old woman named Rose DeWitt Bukater tells the story to her granddaughter Lizzy Calvert, Brock Lovett, Lewis Bodine, Bobby Buell and Anatoly Mikailavich on the Keldysh about her life set in April 10th 1912, on a ship called Titanic when young Rose boards the departing ship with the upper-class passengers and her mother, Ruth DeWitt Bukater, and her fiancÃ©, Caledon Hockley. Meanwhile, a drifter and artist named Jack Dawson and his best friend Fabrizio De Rossi win third-class tickets to the ship in a game. And she explains the whole story from departure until the death of Titanic on its first and last voyage April 15th, 1912 at 2:20 in the morning.', 'en', '1997-11-18', 'James Cameron', 'Paramount Pictures', '194 minutes', '200000000', '1845034188', 9, 'One of the very best romantic movies ....', 'Nothing on Earth could come between them.', '2017-07-01 03:37:28'),
(164, '454', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0117509', 'Romeo + Juliet', 1996, 'images/454 poster.jpg', 6.7, 'images/454 cover.jpg', 'In director Baz Luhrmann''s contemporary take on William Shakespeare''s classic tragedy, the Montagues and Capulets have moved their ongoing feud to the sweltering suburb of Verona Beach, where Romeo and Juliet fall in love and secretly wed. Though the film is visually modern, the bard''s dialogue remains.', 'en', '1996-10-31', 'Baz Luhrmann', 'Bazmark Films', '120 minutes', '14500000', '147298761', 6, '', 'My only love sprung from my only hate.', '2017-07-01 03:38:45'),
(165, '4347', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0783233', 'Atonement', 2007, 'images/4347 poster.jpg', 7.4, 'images/4347 cover.jpg', 'As a 13-year-old, fledgling writer Briony Tallis irrevocably changes the course of several lives when she accuses her older sister''s lover of a crime he did not commit.', 'en', '2007-08-29', 'Joe Wright', 'Universal Pictures', '123 minutes', '30000000', '129266061', 7, 'Tragic .....', 'Torn apart by betrayal. Separated by war. Bound by love.', '2017-07-01 03:43:03'),
(166, '38', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0338013', 'Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind', 2004, 'images/38 poster.jpg', 7.9, 'images/38 cover.jpg', 'Joel Barish, heartbroken that his girlfriend underwent a procedure to erase him from her memory, decides to do the same. However, as he watches his memories of her fade away, he realises that he still loves her, and may be too late to correct his mistake.', 'en', '2004-03-19', 'Michel Gondry', 'Anonymous Content', '108 minutes', '20000000', '72258126', 5, ' Didn''t get it ...', 'You can erase someone from your mind. Getting them out of your heart is another story.', '2017-07-01 03:44:10'),
(167, '19913', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1022603', '(500) Days of Summer', 2009, 'images/19913 poster.jpg', 7.2, 'images/19913 cover.jpg', 'Tom (Joseph Gordon-Levitt), greeting-card writer and hopeless romantic, is caught completely off-guard when his girlfriend, Summer (Zooey Deschanel), suddenly dumps him. He reflects on their 500 days together to try to figure out where their love affair went sour, and in doing so, Tom rediscovers his true passions in life.', 'en', '2009-07-17', 'Marc Webb', 'Fox Searchlight Pictures', '95 minutes', '7500000', '60722734', 6, ' ', 'It was almost like falling in love.', '2009-07-17 00:00:00'),
