(170, '11036', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0332280', 'The Notebook', 2004, 'images/11036 poster.jpg', 7.6, 'images/11036 cover.jpg', 'An epic love story centered around an older man who reads aloud to a woman with Alzheimer''s. From a faded notebook, the old man''s words bring to life the story about a couple who is separated by World War II, and is then passionately reunited, seven years later, after they have taken different paths.', 'en', '2004-06-25', 'Nick Cassavetes', 'New Line Cinema', '123 minutes', '29000000', '115603229', 9, '  One of the best romantic movie ever ...', 'Behind every great love is a great story.', '2017-07-01 03:47:30'),
(171, '22971', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0989757', 'Dear John', 2010, 'images/22971 poster.jpg', 6.5, 'images/22971 cover.jpg', 'Sergeant John Tyree is home on a 2 week leave from Germany. He meets Savannah after he dives into the ocean to retrieve Savannah''s purse that had fallen off the pier. John falls in love with Savannah who is a student on spring break helping build a house for Habitat for Humanity. A romance occurs and Savannah falls deeply in love with John. She promises to write John overseas until he returns.', 'en', '2010-02-04', 'Lasse HallstrÃ¶m', 'Screen Gems', '115 minutes', '25000000', '114977104', 5, ' Ugggggggggggghhhhhhhhhh', 'Love brought them together. Will fate tear them apart?', '2017-07-01 03:48:35'),
(172, '50646', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1570728', 'Crazy, Stupid, Love.', 2011, 'images/50646 poster.jpg', 7, 'images/50646 cover.jpg', 'Cal Weaver is living the American dream. He has a good job, a beautiful house, great children and a beautiful wife, named Emily. Cal''s seemingly perfect life unravels, however, when he learns that Emily has been unfaithful and wants a divorce. Over 40 and suddenly single, Cal is adrift in the fickle world of dating. Enter, Jacob Palmer, a self-styled player who takes Cal under his wing and teaches him how to be a hit with the ladies.', 'en', '2011-07-29', 'Glenn Ficarra', 'Warner Bros.', '118 minutes', '50000000', '142851197', 8, 'great comedy ....', 'This Is Stupid', '2017-07-01 03:49:23'),
(173, '10229', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0281358', 'A Walk to Remember', 2002, 'images/10229 poster.jpg', 7.4, 'images/10229 cover.jpg', 'When the popular, restless Landon Carter is forced to participate in the school drama production he falls in love with Jamie Sullivan, the daughter of the town''s minister. Jamie has a ', 'en', '2002-01-25', 'Adam Shankman', 'DiNovi Pictures', '101 minutes', '11000000', '41227069', 8, ' ', 'She didn''t belong. She was misunderstood. And she would change him forever.', '2017-07-01 03:50:48'),
(174, '222935', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2582846', 'The Fault in Our Stars', 2014, 'images/222935 poster.jpg', 7.7, 'images/222935 cover.jpg', 'Despite the tumor-shrinking medical miracle that has bought her a few years, Hazel has never been anything but terminal, her final chapter inscribed upon diagnosis. But when a patient named Augustus Waters suddenly appears at Cancer Kid Support Group, Hazel''s story is about to be completely rewritten.', 'en', '2014-05-16', 'Josh Boone', 'Fox 2000 Pictures', '125 minutes', '12000000', '307166834', 7, '', 'One Sick Love Story', '2017-07-01 03:51:18'),
(175, '50544', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1632708', 'Friends with Benefits', 2011, 'images/50544 poster.jpg', 6.5, 'images/50544 cover.jpg', 'Jamie is a New York-based executive recruiter who entices Dylan, an art director from Los Angeles, to take a job at the New York office of GQ magazine. Finding that they have much in common, the two become fast friends. Feeling jaded by a number of broken romances, Dylan and Jamie decide that they are ready to quit looking for true love and focus on having fun. However, complications unfold when the two best pals add sex to their relationship.', 'en', '2011-07-21', 'Will Gluck', 'Castle Rock Entertainment', '109 minutes', '35000000', '150483765', 6, '', 'Some friends come with a happy ending.', '2017-07-01 03:52:25'),
(176, '77877', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1327194', 'The Lucky One', 2012, 'images/77877 poster.jpg', 6.8, 'images/77877 cover.jpg', 'U.S. Marine Sergeant Logan Thibault returns from his third tour of duty in Iraq, with the one thing he credits with keeping him alive-a photograph he found of a woman he doesn''t even know. Learning her name is Beth and where she lives, he shows up at her door, and ends up taking a job at her family-run local kennel. Despite her initial mistrust and the complications in her life, a romance develops between them, giving Logan hope that Beth could be much more than his good luck charm.', 'en', '2012-04-19', 'Scott Hicks', 'Village Roadshow Pictures', '101 minutes', '25000000', '99357138', 6, '', '', '2017-07-01 03:53:13');
