(180, '20943', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1142988', 'The Ugly Truth', 2009, 'images/20943 poster.jpg', 6.3, 'images/20943 cover.jpg', 'A romantically challenged morning show producer is reluctantly embroiled in a series of outrageous tests by her chauvinistic correspondent to prove his theories on relationships and help her find love. His clever ploys, however, lead to an unexpected result.', 'en', '2009-07-24', 'Robert Luketic', 'Lakeshore Entertainment', '96 minutes', '38000000', '205298907', 6, '', 'The battle of the sexes is on.', '2017-07-01 03:55:26'),
(181, '38408', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1055292', 'Life As We Know It', 2010, 'images/38408 poster.jpg', 6.5, 'images/38408 cover.jpg', 'After a distastrous first date for caterer Holly and network sports director Messer, all they have is common is a dislike for each other and their love for their goddaughter Sophie. But when they suddenly become all Sophie has in this world, Holly and Messer must set their differences aside. Juggling careers and social calendars, they''ll have to find common ground while living under the same roof.', 'en', '2010-10-02', 'Greg Berlanti', 'Josephson Entertainment', '114 minutes', '38000000', '105610124', 7, '', 'A comedy about taking it one step at a time.', '2017-07-01 03:55:54'),
(182, '27573', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1038919', 'The Bounty Hunter', 2010, 'images/27573 poster.jpg', 5.5, 'images/27573 cover.jpg', 'Milo Boyd is a bounty hunter whose latest gig is rather satisfying, as he finds out that the bail-skipper he must chase down is his own ex-wife, Nicole -- but she has no intention of getting nabbed without a fight. Complicating matters, Nicole''s wannabe-boyfriend, Stewart, joins the chase.', 'en', '2010-03-16', 'Andy Tennant', 'Columbia Pictures', '110 minutes', '40000000', '136000000', 5, '', 'It''s a Job. It Isn''t Personal. Well, Maybe a Little...', '2017-07-01 03:56:52'),
(183, '37821', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1103153', 'Killers', 2010, 'images/37821 poster.jpg', 5.6, 'images/37821 cover.jpg', 'When an elite assassin marries a beautiful computer whiz after a whirlwind romance, he gives up the gun and settles down with his new bride. That is, until he learns that someone from his past has put a contract out on his life.', 'en', '2010-06-04', 'Robert Luketic', 'Katalyst Films', '100 minutes', '75000000', '98159963', 6, '', 'Perfect wife. Perfect target.', '2017-07-01 03:58:15'),
