(313, '956', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0317919', 'Mission: Impossible III', 2006, 'images/956 poster.jpg', 6.5, 'images/956 cover.jpg', 'Retired from active duty to train new IMF agents, Ethan Hunt is called back into action to confront sadistic arms dealer, Owen Davian. Hunt must try to protect his girlfriend while working with his new team to complete the mission.', 'en', '2006-05-03', 'J.J. Abrams', 'Paramount Pictures', '126 minutes', '150000000', '397850012', 7, ' This movie made me a fan of Mission: Impossible series ..', 'The Mission Begins 05:05:06.', '2006-05-03 00:00:00'),
(314, '955', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120755', 'Mission: Impossible II', 2000, 'images/955 poster.jpg', 5.9, 'images/955 cover.jpg', 'With computer genius Luther Stickell at his side and a beautiful thief on his mind, agent Ethan Hunt races across Australia and Spain to stop a former IMF agent from unleashing a genetically engineered biological weapon called Chimera. This mission, should Hunt choose to accept it, plunges him into the center of an international crisis of terrifying magnitude.', 'en', '2000-05-24', 'John Woo', 'Paramount Pictures', '123 minutes', '125000000', '546388105', 6, ' ', 'Expect the impossible again.', '2000-05-24 00:00:00'),
(315, '787', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0356910', 'Mr. & Mrs. Smith', 2005, 'images/787 poster.jpg', 6.5, 'images/787 cover.jpg', 'After five (or six) years of vanilla-wedded bliss, ordinary suburbanites John and Jane Smith are stuck in a huge rut. Unbeknownst to each other, they are both coolly lethal, highly-paid assassins working for rival organisations. When they discover they''re each other''s next target, their secret lives collide in a spicy, explosive mix of wicked comedy, pent-up passion, nonstop action and high-tech weaponry.', 'en', '2005-06-07', 'Doug Liman', 'Weed Road Pictures', '120 minutes', '110000000', '478207520', 8, ' ', 'Smart and sexy.', '2005-06-07 00:00:00'),
(316, '1593', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0477347', 'Night at the Museum', 2006, 'images/1593 poster.jpg', 6.3, 'images/1593 cover.jpg', 'Chaos reigns at the natural history museum when night watchman Larry Daley accidentally stirs up an ancient curse, awakening Attila the Hun, an army of gladiators, a Tyrannosaurus rex and other exhibits. Larry tries desperately to keep the museum under control, but he''s fighting a losing battle until President Teddy Roosevelt comes to the rescue.', 'en', '2006-10-20', 'Shawn Levy', 'Ingenious Film Partners', '108 minutes', '110000000', '574480841', 6, ' ', 'Where History Comes To Life', '2006-10-20 00:00:00'),
(317, '181533', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2692250', 'Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb', 2014, 'images/181533 poster.jpg', 6.1, 'images/181533 cover.jpg', 'When the magic powers of The Tablet of Ahkmenrah begin to die out, Larry Daley (Ben Stiller) spans the globe, uniting favorite and new characters while embarking on an epic quest to save the magic before it is gone forever.', 'en', '2014-12-17', 'Shawn Levy', 'Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation', '97 minutes', '127000000', '349424282', 7, '  ', 'One Final Night to Save the Day.', '2014-12-17 00:00:00'),
(318, '18360', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1078912', 'Night at the Museum: Battle of the Smithsonian', 2009, 'images/18360 poster.jpg', 5.9, 'images/18360 cover.jpg', 'Hapless museum night watchman Larry Daley must help his living, breathing exhibit friends out of a pickle now that they''ve been transferred to the archives at the Smithsonian Institution. Larry''s (mis)adventures this time include close encounters with Amelia Earhart, Abe Lincoln and Ivan the Terrible.', 'en', '2009-05-20', 'Shawn Levy', 'Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation', '105 minutes', '150000000', '413106170', 6, ' ', 'When the lights go off the battle is on.', '2009-05-20 00:00:00'),
(319, '161', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0240772', 'Ocean''s Eleven', 2001, 'images/161 poster.jpg', 7.1, 'images/161 cover.jpg', 'Less than 24 hours into his parole, charismatic thief Danny Ocean is already rolling out his next plan: In one night, Danny''s hand-picked crew of specialists will attempt to steal more than $150 million from three Las Vegas casinos. But to score the cash, Danny risks his chances of reconciling with ex-wife, Tess.', 'en', '2001-12-07', 'Steven Soderbergh', 'Village Roadshow Pictures', '116 minutes', '85000000', '450717150', 8, ' ', 'Are you in or out?', '2001-12-07 00:00:00'),
(320, '298', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0496806', 'Ocean''s Thirteen', 2007, 'images/298 poster.jpg', 6.5, 'images/298 cover.jpg', 'Danny Ocean''s team of criminals are back and are composing a plan more personal than ever. When ruthless casino owner Willy Bank double-crosses Reuben Tishkoff, causing a heart attack, Danny Ocean vows that him and his team will do anything to bring Willy Bank and everything he''s got down. Even if it includes hiring help from one of their own enemies, Terry Benedict.', 'en', '2007-06-07', 'Steven Soderbergh', 'Village Roadshow Pictures', '122 minutes', '85000000', '311312624', 7, ' ', 'What are the odds of getting even? 13 to one.', '2007-06-07 00:00:00'),
(321, '163', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0349903', 'Ocean''s Twelve', 2004, 'images/163 poster.jpg', 6.4, 'images/163 cover.jpg', 'Danny Ocean reunites with his old flame and the rest of his merry band of thieves in carrying out three huge heists in Rome, Paris and Amsterdam â€“ but a Europol agent is hot on their heels.', 'en', '2004-12-09', 'Steven Soderbergh', 'Village Roadshow Pictures', '125 minutes', '110000000', '362744280', 7, '', 'Twelve is the new eleven.', '2017-07-08 18:12:06'),
(322, '274870', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1355644', 'Passengers', 2016, 'images/274870 poster.jpg', 6.6, 'images/274870 cover.jpg', 'A spacecraft traveling to a distant colony planet and transporting thousands of people has a malfunction in its sleep chambers. As a result, two passengers are awakened 90 years early.', 'en', '2016-12-21', 'Morten Tyldum', 'Columbia Pictures', '116 minutes', '110000000', '303144152', 7, '', 'There is a reason they woke up.', '2017-07-08 18:12:42'),
(323, '288036', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3165612', 'Sleeping with Other People', 2015, 'images/288036 poster.jpg', 6.1, 'images/288036 cover.jpg', 'Can two serial cheaters get a second chance at love? After a one-night stand in college, New Yorkers Lainey and Jake meet by chance twelve years later and discover they each have the same problem: because of their monogamy-challenged ways, neither can maintain a relationship. Determined to stay friends despite their mutual attraction, they make a pact to keep it platonic, a deal that proves easier said than done.', 'en', '2015-06-26', 'Leslye Headland', 'Sidney Kimmel Entertainment', '100 minutes', 'unknown', '3214116', 7, '', 'A romantic comedy with commitment issues.', '2017-07-08 18:13:27'),
(324, '243683', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2626350', 'Step Up All In', 2014, 'images/243683 poster.jpg', 6.7, 'images/243683 cover.jpg', 'All-stars from the previous Step Up installments come together in glittering Las Vegas, battling for a victory that could define their dreams and their careers.', 'en', '2014-07-16', 'Trish Sie', 'Summit Entertainment', '112 minutes', '45000000', '86165646', 6, ' ', 'Every Step Has Led To This', '2014-07-16 00:00:00'),
(325, '9762', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0462590', 'Step Up', 2006, 'images/9762 poster.jpg', 6.7, 'images/9762 cover.jpg', 'Everyone deserves a chance to follow their dreams, but some people only get one shot. Tyler Gage is a rebel from the wrong side of Baltimore''s tracks and the only thing that stands between him and an unfulfilled life are his dreams of one day making it out of there. Nora is a privileged ballet dancer attending Baltimore''s ultra-elite Maryland School of the Arts', 'en', '2006-08-11', 'Anne Fletcher', 'Summit Entertainment', '104 minutes', '12000000', '114194847', 6, ' ', 'Every Second Chance Begins With a First Step', '2006-08-11 00:00:00'),
(326, '85446', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1800741', 'Step Up Revolution', 2012, 'images/85446 poster.jpg', 6.6, 'images/85446 cover.jpg', 'Emily arrives in Miami with aspirations to become a professional dancer. She sparks with Sean, the leader of a dance crew whose neighborhood is threatened by Emily''s father''s development plans.', 'en', '2012-07-26', 'Scott Speer', 'Summit Entertainment', '99 minutes', '33000000', '140470746', 6, ' ', 'One Step Can Change Your World', '2012-07-26 00:00:00'),
(327, '41233', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1193631', 'Step Up 3D', 2010, 'images/41233 poster.jpg', 6.6, 'images/41233 cover.jpg', 'A tight-knit group of New York City street dancers, including Luke and Natalie, team up with NYU freshman Moose, and find themselves pitted against the world''s best hip hop dancers in a high-stakes showdown that will change their lives forever.', 'en', '2010-08-04', 'Jon M. Chu', 'Summit Entertainment', '107 minutes', '30000000', '159291809', 7, ' Mooseeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee', 'Two Worlds. One Dream.', '2010-08-04 00:00:00'),
(328, '34544', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0429493', 'The A-Team', 2010, 'images/34544 poster.jpg', 6.2, 'images/34544 cover.jpg', 'A group of Iraq War veterans goes on the run from U.S. military forces while they try to clear their names after being framed for a crime they didn''t commit. Along the way, Col. Hannibal Smith, Capt. H.M. â€˜Howling Madâ€™ Murdock , Sgt. Bosco â€˜B.A.â€™ Baracus, and Lt. Templeton â€˜Facemanâ€™ Peck help out various people they encounter.', 'en', '2010-06-10', 'Joe Carnahan', 'Ingenious Film Partners', '117 minutes', '110000000', '177238796', 7, ' ', 'There Is No Plan B', '2010-06-10 00:00:00'),
(329, '24428', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0848228', 'The Avengers', 2012, 'images/24428 poster.jpg', 7.4, 'images/24428 cover.jpg', 'When an unexpected enemy emerges and threatens global safety and security, Nick Fury, director of the international peacekeeping agency known as S.H.I.E.L.D., finds himself in need of a team to pull the world back from the brink of disaster. Spanning the globe, a daring recruitment effort begins!', 'en', '2012-04-25', 'Joss Whedon', 'Paramount Pictures', '143 minutes', '220000000', '1519557910', 10, '     Every minute of this movie is enjoyable..... ', 'Some assembly required.', '2012-04-25 00:00:00'),
(330, '14832', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0106535', 'The Cement Garden', 1993, 'images/14832 poster.jpg', 7.1, 'images/14832 cover.jpg', 'After the death of her husband, the mother of Julie, Jack, Sue and Tom begins to suffer from a mysterious illness. Aware that she is going to have to go into hospital she opens a bank account for the children, so that they can be financially self-sufficient and will be able to avoid being taken into care by the authorities. Unfortunately she also dies and Julie and Jack (the older, teenage children) decide to hide her body in the basement so that they can have free reign of their household. Soon Tom has taken to dressing as a girl whilst Sue has become increasingly reticent, confiding only to her diary, meanwhile Jack and Julie sense an attraction developing for each other. However Julie''s new beau, Derek, threatens to unearth the many dark secrets within this family as he becomes increasingly suspicious of Jack.', 'en', '1993-02-05', 'Andrew Birkin', 'Zweites Deutsches Fernsehen (ZDF)', '105 minutes', 'unknown', '322975', 8, '', 'Love knows no limits.', '2017-07-08 18:20:09'),
(331, '330483', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3797868', 'The Choice', 2016, 'images/330483 poster.jpg', 6.6, 'images/330483 cover.jpg', 'Travis and Gabby first meet as neighbors in a small coastal town and wind up in a relationship that is tested by life''s most defining events.', 'en', '2016-02-04', 'Ross Katz', 'Lionsgate', '111 minutes', '10000000', 'unknown', 7, '', 'Let your heart decide.', '2017-07-08 18:20:32'),
(332, '259693', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3065204', 'The Conjuring 2', 2016, 'images/259693 poster.jpg', 6.9, 'images/259693 cover.jpg', 'Lorraine and Ed Warren travel to north London to help a single mother raising four children alone in a house plagued by malicious spirits.', 'en', '2016-05-13', 'James Wan', 'New Line Cinema', '134 minutes', '40000000', '320170008', 7, 'Loved it despite being a horror ...', 'The next true story from the case files of Ed and Lorraine Warren', '2017-07-08 18:21:19');
