(366, '10191', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0892769', 'How to Train Your Dragon', 2010, 'images/10191 poster.jpg', 7.5, 'images/10191 cover.jpg', 'As the son of a Viking leader on the cusp of manhood, shy Hiccup Horrendous Haddock III faces a rite of passage: he must kill a dragon to prove his warrior mettle. But after downing a feared dragon, he realizes that he no longer wants to destroy it, and instead befriends the beast â€“ which he names Toothless â€“ much to the chagrin of his warrior father', 'en', '2010-03-05', 'Dean DeBlois', 'DreamWorks Animation', '98 minutes', '165000000', '494878759', 8, ' To me the best animation movie...', 'One adventure will change two worlds', '2010-03-05 00:00:00'),
(367, '82702', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1646971', 'How to Train Your Dragon 2', 2014, 'images/82702 poster.jpg', 7.7, 'images/82702 cover.jpg', 'The thrilling second chapter of the epic How To Train Your Dragon trilogy brings back the fantastical world of Hiccup and Toothless five years later. While Astrid, Snotlout and the rest of the gang are challenging each other to dragon races (the island''s new favorite contact sport), the now inseparable pair journey through the skies, charting unmapped territories and exploring new worlds. When one of their adventures leads to the discovery of a secret ice cave that is home to hundreds of new wild dragons and the mysterious Dragon Rider, the two friends find themselves at the center of a battle to protect the peace.', 'en', '2014-06-12', 'Dean DeBlois', 'DreamWorks Animation', '102 minutes', '145000000', '609123048', 8, ' ', 'The training is over.', '2014-06-12 00:00:00'),
