(370, '1735', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0859163', 'The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor', 2008, 'images/1735 poster.jpg', 5.2, 'images/1735 cover.jpg', 'Archaeologist Rick O''Connell travels to China, pitting him against an emperor from the 2,000-year-old Han dynasty who''s returned from the dead to pursue a quest for world domination. This time, O''Connell enlists the help of his wife and son to quash the so-called ''Dragon Emperor'' and his abuse of supernatural power.', 'en', '2008-07-01', 'Rob Cohen', 'Universal Pictures', '112 minutes', '145000000', '401128639', 6, ' ', 'A New Evil Awakens.', '2008-07-01 00:00:00'),
(371, '1487', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0167190', 'Hellboy', 2004, 'images/1487 poster.jpg', 6.5, 'images/1487 cover.jpg', 'In the final days of World War II, the Nazis attempt to use black magic to aid their dying cause. The Allies raid the camp where the ceremony is taking place, but not before a demon - Hellboy - has already been conjured. Joining the Allied forces, Hellboy eventually grows to adulthood, serving the cause of good rather than evil.', 'en', '2004-04-02', 'Guillermo del Toro', 'Revolution Studios', '122 minutes', '66000000', '99318987', 6, ' ', 'From the Dark Side to Our Side.', '2004-04-02 00:00:00'),
