(466, '64635', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1386703', 'Total Recall', 2012, 'images/64635 poster.jpg', 5.8, 'images/64635 cover.jpg', 'Welcome to Rekall, the company that can turn your dreams into real memories. For a factory worker named Douglas Quaid, even though he''s got a beautiful wife who he loves, the mind-trip sounds like the perfect vacation from his frustrating life - real memories of life as a super-spy might be just what he needs. But when the procedure goes horribly wrong, Quaid becomes a hunted man. Finding himself on the run from the police - controlled by Chancellor Cohaagen, the leader of the free world - Quaid teams up with a rebel fighter to find the head of the underground resistance and stop Cohaagen. The line between fantasy and reality gets blurred and the fate of his world hangs in the balance as Quaid discovers his true identity, his true love, and his true fate.', 'en', '2012-08-02', 'Len Wiseman', 'Columbia Pictures', '121 minutes', '125000000', '198802074', 6, '', 'What Is Real?', '2017-07-10 03:56:15'),
(467, '76163', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1764651', 'The Expendables 2', 2012, 'images/76163 poster.jpg', 6.1, 'images/76163 cover.jpg', 'Mr. Church reunites the Expendables for what should be an easy paycheck, but when one of their men is murdered on the job, their quest for revenge puts them deep in enemy territory and up against an unexpected threat.', 'en', '2012-08-08', 'Simon West', 'Nu Image Films', '103 minutes', '100000000', '312573423', 6, ' ', 'Back for War.', '2012-08-08 00:00:00'),
(468, '27578', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1320253', 'The Expendables', 2010, 'images/27578 poster.jpg', 6, 'images/27578 cover.jpg', 'Barney Ross leads a band of highly skilled mercenaries including knife enthusiast Lee Christmas, a martial arts expert, heavy weapons specialist, demolitionist, and a loose-cannon sniper. When the group is commissioned by the mysterious Mr. Church to assassinate the dictator of a small South American island, Barney and Lee visit the remote locale to scout out their opposition and discover the true nature of the conflict engulfing the city.', 'en', '2010-08-03', 'Sylvester Stallone', 'Millennium Films', '103 minutes', '80000000', '274470394', 5, ' ', 'Choose Your Weapon.', '2010-08-03 00:00:00'),
(469, '14869', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1046173', 'G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra', 2009, 'images/14869 poster.jpg', 5.6, 'images/14869 cover.jpg', 'From the Egyptian desert to deep below the polar ice caps, the elite G.I. JOE team uses the latest in next-generation spy and military equipment to fight the corrupt arms dealer Destro and the growing threat of the mysterious Cobra organization to prevent them from plunging the world into chaos.', 'en', '2009-08-04', 'Stephen Sommers', 'Paramount Pictures', '118 minutes', '175000000', '302469017', 6, ' ', 'When all else fails, they don''t.', '2009-08-04 00:00:00'),
(470, '72559', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1583421', 'G.I. Joe: Retaliation', 2013, 'images/72559 poster.jpg', 5.4, 'images/72559 cover.jpg', 'Framed for crimes against the country, the G.I. Joe team is terminated by Presidential order. This forces the G.I. Joes into not only fighting their mortal enemy Cobra; they are forced to contend with threats from within the government that jeopardize their very existence.', 'en', '2013-03-26', 'Jon M. Chu', 'Paramount Pictures', '110 minutes', '130000000', '371876278', 5, ' ', '', '2013-03-26 00:00:00'),
(471, '72331', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1611224', 'Abraham Lincoln: Vampire Hunter', 2012, 'images/72331 poster.jpg', 5.5, 'images/72331 cover.jpg', 'President Lincoln''s mother is killed by a supernatural creature, which fuels his passion to crush vampires and their slave-owning helpers.', 'en', '2012-06-20', 'Timur Bekmambetov', 'Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation', '94 minutes', '69000000', '112265139', 6, ' ', 'Are you a patriot or a vampire?', '2012-06-20 00:00:00'),
(472, '38575', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1155076', 'The Karate Kid', 2010, 'images/38575 poster.jpg', 6.1, 'images/38575 cover.jpg', '12-year-old Dre Parker could have been the most popular kid in Detroit, but his mother''s latest career move has landed him in China. Dre immediately falls for his classmate Mei Ying but the cultural differences make such a friendship impossible. Even worse, Dre''s feelings make him an enemy of the class bully, Cheng. With no friends in a strange land, Dre has nowhere to turn but maintenance man Mr. Han, who is a kung fu master. As Han teaches Dre that kung fu is not about punches and parries, but maturity and calm, Dre realizes that facing down the bullies will be the fight of his life.', 'en', '2010-06-10', 'Harald Zwart', 'Columbia Pictures', '140 minutes', '40000000', '357852395', 5, ' ', 'A Challenge He Never Imagined. A Teacher He Never Expected.', '2010-06-10 00:00:00'),
(473, '38050', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1385826', 'The Adjustment Bureau', 2011, 'images/38050 poster.jpg', 6.5, 'images/38050 cover.jpg', 'A man glimpses the future Fate has planned for him â€“ and chooses to fight for his own destiny. Battling the powerful Adjustment Bureau across, under and through the streets of New York, he risks his destined greatness to be with the only woman he''s ever loved.', 'en', '2011-03-03', 'George Nolfi', 'Universal Pictures', '106 minutes', '50200000', '127869379', 5, '', 'Fight for your fate.', '2017-07-10 04:03:21'),
(474, '1495', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0320661', 'Kingdom of Heaven', 2005, 'images/1495 poster.jpg', 6.5, 'images/1495 cover.jpg', 'After his wife dies, a blacksmith named Balian is thrust into royalty, political intrigue and bloody holy wars during the Crusades.', 'en', '2005-05-03', 'Ridley Scott', 'Studio Babelsberg', '144 minutes', '130000000', '211643158', 6, ' ', 'Be without fear in the face of your enemies. Safeguard the helpless, and do no wrong', '2005-05-03 00:00:00'),
(475, '137113', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1631867', 'Edge of Tomorrow', 2014, 'images/137113 poster.jpg', 7.7, 'images/137113 cover.jpg', 'Major Bill Cage is an officer who has never seen a day of combat when he is unceremoniously demoted and dropped into combat. Cage is killed within minutes, managing to take an alpha alien down with him. He awakens back at the beginning of the same day and is forced to fight and die again... and again - as physical contact with the alien has thrown him into a time loop.', 'en', '2014-05-27', 'Doug Liman', 'Village Roadshow Pictures', '113 minutes', '178000000', '370541256', 7, ' ', 'Live, Die, Repeat', '2014-05-27 00:00:00'),
(476, '58431', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1374989', 'Pride and Prejudice and Zombies', 2016, 'images/58431 poster.jpg', 5.4, 'images/58431 cover.jpg', 'A zombie outbreak has fallen upon the land in this reimagining of Jane Austenâ€™s classic tale of the tangled relationships between lovers from different social classes in 19th century England. Feisty heroine Elizabeth Bennet (Lily James) is a master of martial arts and weaponry and the handsome Mr. Darcy (Sam Riley) is a fierce zombie killer, yet the epitome of upper class prejudice. As the zombie outbreak intensifies, they must swallow their pride and join forces on the blood-soaked battlefield in order to conquer the undead once and for all.', 'en', '2016-02-04', 'Burr Steers', 'Lionsgate', '108 minutes', '28000000', '16374328', 6, '', 'Bloody lovely.', '2017-07-10 04:10:55'),
(477, '245', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0276751', 'About a Boy', 2002, 'images/245 poster.jpg', 6.6, 'images/245 cover.jpg', 'Will Freeman is a hip Londoner who one day realizes that his friends are all involved with the responsibilities of married life and that leaves him alone in the cold. Passing himself off as a single father, he starts to meet a string of single mums, confident in his ability to leave them behind when they start to ask for a commitment. But Will''s hope of a continued bachelorhood is interrupted when he meets 12-year old Marcus, in many ways his complete opposite.', 'en', '2002-04-26', 'Chris Weitz', 'Universal Pictures', '101 minutes', '27000000', '129000000', 6, '', 'One ordinary couple. One little white lie.', '2017-07-11 02:16:16'),
(478, '60308', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1210166', 'Moneyball', 2011, 'images/60308 poster.jpg', 7, 'images/60308 cover.jpg', 'The story of Oakland Athletics general manager Billy Beane''s successful attempt to put together a baseball team on a budget, by employing computer-generated analysis to draft his players.', 'en', '2011-09-22', 'Bennett Miller', 'Columbia Pictures', '133 minutes', '50000000', '110206216', 7, 'I''m just a little ......', 'What are you really worth?', '2017-07-11 03:41:13'),
(479, '51497', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1596343', 'Fast Five', 2011, 'images/51497 poster.jpg', 7.1, 'images/51497 cover.jpg', 'Former cop Brian O''Conner partners with ex-con Dom Toretto on the opposite side of the law. Since Brian and Mia Toretto broke Dom out of custody, they''ve blown across many borders to elude authorities. Now backed into a corner in Rio de Janeiro, they must pull one last job in order to gain their freedom.', 'en', '2011-04-20', 'Justin Lin', 'Universal Pictures', '130 minutes', '125000000', '626137675', 7, ' ', 'Get the Fifth Gear.', '2011-04-20 00:00:00'),
(480, '38356', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1399103', 'Transformers: Dark of the Moon', 2011, 'images/38356 poster.jpg', 6.1, 'images/38356 cover.jpg', 'Sam Witwicky takes his first tenuous steps into adulthood while remaining a reluctant human ally of Autobot-leader Optimus Prime. The film centers around the space race between the USSR and the USA, suggesting there was a hidden Transformers role in it all that remains one of the planet''s most dangerous secrets.', 'en', '2011-06-28', 'Michael Bay', 'Paramount Pictures', '154 minutes', '195000000', '1123746996', 7, ' ', 'The invasion we always feared. An enemy we never expected.', '2011-06-28 00:00:00'),
(481, '37724', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1074638', 'Skyfall', 2012, 'images/37724 poster.jpg', 6.9, 'images/37724 cover.jpg', 'When Bond''s latest assignment goes gravely wrong and agents around the world are exposed, MI6 is attacked forcing M to relocate the agency. These events cause her authority and position to be challenged by Gareth Mallory, the new Chairman of the Intelligence and Security Committee. With MI6 now compromised from both inside and out, M is left with one ally she can trust: Bond. 007 takes to the shadows - aided only by field agent, Eve - following a trail to the mysterious Silva, whose lethal and hidden motives have yet to reveal themselves.', 'en', '2012-10-25', 'Sam Mendes', 'Columbia Pictures', '143 minutes', '200000000', '1108561013', 7, ' ', 'Think on your sins.', '2012-10-25 00:00:00');
