(482, '80038', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1720616', 'Friends with Kids', 2011, 'images/80038 poster.jpg', 5.7, 'images/80038 cover.jpg', 'In the wake of their friends'' marriages and eventual offspring, longtime pals Julie and Jason decide to have a child together without becoming a couple. By becoming ', 'en', '2011-09-09', 'Jennifer Westfeldt', 'Locomotive', '100 minutes', 'unknown', '12186625', 6, '', 'Love. Happiness. Kids. Pick two.', '2017-07-12 02:10:51'),
(483, '61791', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1318514', 'Rise of the Planet of the Apes', 2011, 'images/61791 poster.jpg', 7, 'images/61791 cover.jpg', 'Scientist Will Rodman is determined to find a cure for Alzheimer''s, the disease which has slowly consumed his father. Will feels certain he is close to a breakthrough and tests his latest serum on apes, noticing dramatic increases in intelligence and brain activity in the primate subjects â€“ especially Caesar, his pet chimpanzee.', 'en', '2011-08-03', 'Rupert Wyatt', 'Ingenious Film Partners', '105 minutes', '93000000', '482860185', 6, ' ', 'Evolution Becomes Revolution.', '2011-08-03 00:00:00'),
(484, '119450', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2103281', 'Dawn of the Planet of the Apes', 2014, 'images/119450 poster.jpg', 7.3, 'images/119450 cover.jpg', 'A group of scientists in San Francisco struggle to stay alive in the aftermath of a plague that is wiping out humanity, while Caesar tries to maintain dominance over his community of intelligent apes.', 'en', '2014-06-26', 'Matt Reeves', 'Ingenious Media', '130 minutes', '170000000', '710644566', 6, ' ', 'One last chance for peace.', '2014-06-26 00:00:00'),
(485, '12162', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0887912', 'The Hurt Locker', 2008, 'images/12162 poster.jpg', 7.2, 'images/12162 cover.jpg', 'Forced to play a dangerous game of cat-and-mouse in the chaos of war, an elite Army bomb squad unit must come together in a city where everyone is a potential enemy and every object could be a deadly bomb.', 'en', '2008-10-10', 'Kathryn Bigelow', 'Summit Entertainment', '131 minutes', '15000000', '42000000', 7, ' ', 'You''ll know when you''re in it.', '2008-10-10 00:00:00'),
(486, '12405', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1010048', 'Slumdog Millionaire', 2008, 'images/12405 poster.jpg', 7.6, 'images/12405 cover.jpg', 'Jamal Malik is an impoverished Indian teen who becomes a contestant on the Hindi version of â€˜Who Wants to Be a Millionaire?â€™ but, after he wins, he is suspected of cheating.', 'en', '2008-05-12', 'Danny Boyle', 'Fox Searchlight Pictures', '120 minutes', '15000000', '377910544', 6, '  ', 'What does it take to find a lost love? A. Money, B. Luck, C. Smarts, D. Destiny', '2008-05-12 00:00:00'),
(487, '190859', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2179136', 'American Sniper', 2014, 'images/190859 poster.jpg', 7.4, 'images/190859 cover.jpg', 'U.S. Navy SEAL Chris Kyle takes his sole missionâ€”protect his comradesâ€”to heart and becomes one of the most lethal snipers in American history. His pinpoint accuracy not only saves countless lives but also makes him a prime target of insurgents. Despite grave danger and his struggle to be a good husband and father to his family back in the States, Kyle serves four tours of duty in Iraq. However, when he finally returns home, he finds that he cannot leave the war behind.', 'en', '2014-12-11', 'Clint Eastwood', 'Village Roadshow Pictures', '133 minutes', '58800000', '542307423', 7, ' ', 'The most lethal sniper in U.S. history.', '2014-12-11 00:00:00'),
(488, '87827', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0454876', 'Life of Pi', 2012, 'images/87827 poster.jpg', 7.2, 'images/87827 cover.jpg', 'The story of an Indian boy named Pi, a zookeeper''s son who finds himself in the company of a hyena, zebra, orangutan, and a Bengal tiger after a shipwreck sets them adrift in the Pacific Ocean.', 'en', '2012-11-20', 'Ang Lee', 'Ingenious Film Partners', '127 minutes', '120000000', '609016565', 6, ' ', 'Believe The Unbelievable', '2012-11-20 00:00:00'),
(489, '70160', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1392170', 'The Hunger Games', 2012, 'images/70160 poster.jpg', 6.8, 'images/70160 cover.jpg', 'Every year in the ruins of what was once North America, the nation of Panem forces each of its twelve districts to send a teenage boy and girl to compete in the Hunger Games.  Part twisted entertainment, part government intimidation tactic, the Hunger Games are a nationally televised event in which â€œTributesâ€ must fight with one another until one survivor remains.  Pitted against highly-trained Tributes who have prepared for these Games their entire lives, Katniss is forced to rely upon her sharp instincts as well as the mentorship of drunken former victor Haymitch Abernathy.  If sheâ€™s ever to return home to District 12, Katniss must make impossible choices in the arena that weigh survival against humanity and life against love. The world will be watching.', 'en', '2012-03-12', 'Gary Ross', 'Lionsgate', '142 minutes', '75000000', '691210692', 6, '', 'May The Odds Be Ever In Your Favor.', '2017-07-12 02:32:30'),
(490, '49047', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1454468', 'Gravity', 2013, 'images/49047 poster.jpg', 7.3, 'images/49047 cover.jpg', 'Dr. Ryan Stone, a brilliant medical engineer on her first Shuttle mission, with veteran astronaut Matt Kowalsky in command of his last flight before retiring. But on a seemingly routine spacewalk, disaster strikes. The Shuttle is destroyed, leaving Stone and Kowalsky completely alone-tethered to nothing but each other and spiraling out into the blackness of space. The deafening silence tells them they have lost any link to Earth and any chance for rescue. As fear turns to panic, every gulp of air eats away at what little oxygen is left. But the only way home may be to go further out into the terrifying expanse of space.', 'en', '2013-09-27', 'Alfonso CuarÃ³n', 'Warner Bros.', '91 minutes', '105000000', '716392705', 7, ' ', 'Don''t Let Go', '2013-09-27 00:00:00'),
(491, '240832', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2872732', 'Lucy', 2014, 'images/240832 poster.jpg', 6.2, 'images/240832 cover.jpg', 'A woman, accidentally caught in a dark deal, turns the tables on her captors and transforms into a merciless warrior evolved beyond human logic.', 'en', '2014-07-14', 'Luc Besson', 'Universal Pictures', '89 minutes', '40000000', '126546825', 6, '', 'The average person uses 10% of their brain capacity. Imagine what she could do with 100%.', '2017-07-12 02:41:08'),
(492, '51828', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1563738', 'One Day', 2011, 'images/51828 poster.jpg', 7, 'images/51828 cover.jpg', 'A romantic comedy centered on Dexter and Emma, who first meet during their graduation in 1988 and proceed to keep in touch regularly. The film follows what they do on July 15 annually, usually doing something together.', 'en', '2011-03-02', 'Lone Scherfig', 'Film 4', '107 minutes', '15000000', '59389433', 6, '', 'Twenty years. Two people.', '2017-07-12 02:45:00'),
(493, '276907', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3569230', 'Legend', 2015, 'images/276907 poster.jpg', 6.7, 'images/276907 cover.jpg', 'Suave, charming and volatile, Reggie Kray and his unstable twin brother Ronnie start to leave their mark on the London underworld in the 1960s. Using violence to get what they want, the siblings orchestrate robberies and murders while running nightclubs and protection rackets. With police Detective Leonard ', 'en', '2015-09-09', 'Brian Helgeland', 'Working Title Films', '131 minutes', '25000000', '42972994', 6, '', 'Love, fight, live, rule like a legend.', '2017-07-12 02:45:19'),
(494, '295964', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2503944', 'Burnt', 2015, 'images/295964 poster.jpg', 6.4, 'images/295964 cover.jpg', 'Adam Jones is a Chef who destroyed his career with drugs and diva behavior. He cleans up and returns to London, determined to redeem himself by spearheading a top restaurant that can gain three Michelin stars.', 'en', '2015-10-02', 'John Wells', 'Double Feature Films', '100 minutes', '20000000', '36606743', 6, '', 'Never underestimate a man with everything to lose.', '2017-07-12 02:46:22'),
(495, '82633', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1212450', 'Lawless', 2012, 'images/82633 poster.jpg', 6.8, 'images/82633 cover.jpg', 'Set in the Depression-era Franklin County, Virginia, a bootlegging gang is threatened by authorities who want a cut of their profits.', 'en', '2012-08-29', 'John Hillcoat', 'The Weinstein Company', '115 minutes', '26000000', '53676580', 7, '', 'When the law became corrupt, outlaws became heroes.', '2017-07-12 02:49:38'),
(496, '168672', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1800241', 'American Hustle', 2013, 'images/168672 poster.jpg', 6.8, 'images/168672 cover.jpg', 'A con man, Irving Rosenfeld, along with his seductive partner Sydney Prosser, is forced to work for a wild FBI agent, Richie DiMaso, who pushes them into a world of Jersey powerbrokers and mafia.', 'en', '2013-12-12', 'David O. Russell', 'Columbia Pictures', '138 minutes', '40000000', '251171807', 7, ' ', 'Everyone Hustles To Survive', '2013-12-12 00:00:00'),
(497, '68726', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1663662', 'Pacific Rim', 2013, 'images/68726 poster.jpg', 6.7, 'images/68726 cover.jpg', 'When legions of monstrous creatures, known as Kaiju, started rising from the sea, a war began that would take millions of lives and consume humanity''s resources for years on end. To combat the giant Kaiju, a special type of weapon was devised: massive robots, called Jaegers, which are controlled simultaneously by two pilots whose minds are locked in a neural bridge. But even the Jaegers are proving nearly defenseless in the face of the relentless Kaiju. On the verge of defeat, the forces defending mankind have no choice but to turn to two unlikely heroesâ€”a washed-up former pilot (Charlie Hunnam) and an untested trainee (Rinko Kikuchi)â€”who are teamed to drive a legendary but seemingly obsolete Jaeger from the past. Together, they stand as mankind''s last hope against the mounting apocalypse.', 'en', '2013-07-11', 'Guillermo del Toro', 'Legendary Pictures', '131 minutes', '180000000', '407602906', 7, ' ', 'To Fight Monsters, We Created Monsters', '2013-07-11 00:00:00'),
(498, '49521', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0770828', 'Man of Steel', 2013, 'images/49521 poster.jpg', 6.5, 'images/49521 cover.jpg', 'A young boy learns that he has extraordinary powers and is not of this earth. As a young man, he journeys to discover where he came from and what he was sent here to do. But the hero in him must emerge if he is to save the world from annihilation and become the symbol of hope for all mankind.', 'en', '2013-06-12', 'Zack Snyder', 'Legendary Pictures', '143 minutes', '225000000', '662845518', 7, ' ', 'You will believe that a man can fly.', '2013-06-12 00:00:00'),
(499, '80', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0381681', 'Before Sunset', 2004, 'images/80 poster.jpg', 7.6, 'images/80 cover.jpg', 'Nine years ago two strangers met by chance and spent a night in Vienna that ended before sunrise. They are about to meet for the first time since. Now they have one afternoon to find out if they belong together.', 'en', '2004-02-10', 'Richard Linklater', 'Castle Rock Entertainment', '80 minutes', '2700000', '15992615', 6, ' ', 'What if you had a second chance with the one that got away?', '2004-02-10 00:00:00'),
(500, '72190', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0816711', 'World War Z', 2013, 'images/72190 poster.jpg', 6.7, 'images/72190 cover.jpg', 'Life for former United Nations investigator Gerry Lane and his family seems content. Suddenly, the world is plagued by a mysterious infection turning whole human populations into rampaging mindless zombies. After barely escaping the chaos, Lane is persuaded to go on a mission to investigate this disease. What follows is a perilous trek around the world where Lane must brave horrific dangers and long odds to find answers before human civilization falls.', 'en', '2013-06-20', 'Marc Forster', 'Paramount Pictures', '116 minutes', '200000000', '531865000', 7, ' ', 'Remember Philly!', '2013-06-20 00:00:00'),
(501, '9799', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0232500', 'The Fast and the Furious', 2001, 'images/9799 poster.jpg', 6.5, 'images/9799 cover.jpg', 'Domenic Toretto is a Los Angeles street racer suspected of masterminding a series of big-rig hijackings. When undercover cop Brian O''Conner infiltrates Toretto''s iconoclastic crew, he falls for Toretto''s sister and must choose a side: the gang or the LAPD.', 'en', '2001-06-22', 'Rob Cohen', 'Universal Pictures', '106 minutes', '38000000', '207283925', 7, ' ', 'Live life 1/4 mile at a time.', '2001-06-22 00:00:00'),
(502, '584', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0322259', '2 Fast 2 Furious', 2003, 'images/584 poster.jpg', 6.1, 'images/584 cover.jpg', 'It''s a major double-cross when former police officer Brian O''Conner teams up with his ex-con buddy Roman Pearce to transport a shipment of ', 'en', '2003-06-05', 'John Singleton', 'Mikona Productions GmbH & Co. KG', '107 minutes', '76000000', '236350661', 6, ' ', 'How Fast Do You Want It?', '2003-06-05 00:00:00'),
(503, '9615', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0463985', 'The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift', 2006, 'images/9615 poster.jpg', 6.1, 'images/9615 cover.jpg', 'In order to avoid a jail sentence, Sean Boswell heads to Tokyo to live with his military father. In a low-rent section of the city, Shaun gets caught up in the underground world of drift racing', 'en', '2006-06-03', 'Justin Lin', 'Universal Pictures', '104 minutes', '85000000', '158468292', 6, '  ', 'On the streets of Tokyo, speed needs no translation...', '2006-06-03 00:00:00'),
(504, '57201', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1210819', 'The Lone Ranger', 2013, 'images/57201 poster.jpg', 6, 'images/57201 cover.jpg', 'The Texas Rangers chase down a gang of outlaws led by Butch Cavendish, but the gang ambushes the Rangers, seemingly killing them all. One survivor is found, however, by an American Indian named Tonto, who nurses him back to health. The Ranger, donning a mask and riding a white stallion named Silver, teams up with Tonto to bring the unscrupulous gang and others of that ilk to justice.', 'en', '2013-07-03', 'Gore Verbinski', 'Walt Disney Pictures', '149 minutes', '255000000', '89289910', 6, ' ', 'Never Take Off the Mask', '2013-07-03 00:00:00'),
(505, '124905', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0831387', 'Godzilla', 2014, 'images/124905 poster.jpg', 6.1, 'images/124905 cover.jpg', 'Ford Brody, a Navy bomb expert, has just reunited with his family in San Francisco when he is forced to go to Japan to help his estranged father, Joe. Soon, both men are swept up in an escalating crisis when Godzilla, King of the Monsters, arises from the sea to combat malevolent adversaries that threaten the survival of humanity. The creatures leave colossal destruction in their wake, as they make their way toward their final battleground: San Francisco.', 'en', '2014-05-14', 'Gareth Edwards', 'Toho Company', '123 minutes', '160000000', '529076069', 6, ' ', 'The king will rise.', '2014-05-14 00:00:00'),
