(509, '264660', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0470752', 'Ex Machina', 2015, 'images/264660 poster.jpg', 7.6, 'images/264660 cover.jpg', 'Caleb, a 26 year old coder at the world''s largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact with the world''s first true artificial intelligence, housed in the body of a beautiful robot girl.', 'en', '2015-01-21', 'Alex Garland', 'DNA Films', '108 minutes', '15000000', '36869414', 7, ' ', 'There is nothing more human than the will to survive', '2015-01-21 00:00:00'),
(510, '286554', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2140619', 'Two Night Stand', 2014, 'images/286554 poster.jpg', 6.3, 'images/286554 cover.jpg', 'After an extremely regrettable one night stand, two strangers wake up to find themselves snowed in after sleeping through a blizzard that put all of Manhattan on ice. They''re now trapped together in a tiny apartment, forced to get to know each other way more than any one night stand should.', 'en', '2014-09-26', 'Max Nichols', 'Demarest Films', '86 minutes', 'unknown', '18612', 6, '', 'Before love. After sex.', '2017-07-12 03:12:53'),
(511, '216015', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2322441', 'Fifty Shades of Grey', 2015, 'images/216015 poster.jpg', 5.2, 'images/216015 cover.jpg', 'When college senior Anastasia Steele steps in for her sick roommate to interview prominent businessman Christian Grey for their campus paper, little does she realize the path her life will take. Christian, as enigmatic as he is rich and powerful, finds himself strangely drawn to Ana, and she to him. Though sexually inexperienced, Ana plunges headlong into an affair -- and learns that Christian''s true sexual proclivities push the boundaries of pain and pleasure.', 'en', '2015-02-11', 'Sam Taylor-Johnson', 'Focus Features', '125 minutes', '40000000', '571006128', 5, ' ', 'Are you curious?', '2015-02-11 00:00:00'),
(512, '297761', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1386697', 'Suicide Squad', 2016, 'images/297761 poster.jpg', 5.9, 'images/297761 cover.jpg', 'From DC Comics comes the Suicide Squad, an antihero team of incarcerated supervillains who act as deniable assets for the United States government, undertaking high-risk black ops missions in exchange for commuted prison sentences.', 'en', '2016-08-02', 'David Ayer', 'DC Comics', '123 minutes', '175000000', '745000000', 6, '', 'Worst Heroes Ever', '2017-07-12 03:19:50'),
(513, '259316', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3183660', 'Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them', 2016, 'images/259316 poster.jpg', 7.1, 'images/259316 cover.jpg', 'In 1926, Newt Scamander arrives at the Magical Congress of the United States of America with a magically expanded briefcase, which houses a number of dangerous creatures and their habitats. When the creatures escape from the briefcase, it sends the American wizarding authorities after Newt, and threatens to strain even further the state of magical and non-magical relations.', 'en', '2016-11-16', 'David Yates', 'Heyday films', '133 minutes', '180000000', '809342332', 6, '  ', 'From J.K. Rowling''s wizarding world.', '2017-07-12 03:21:25'),
(514, '8960', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0448157', 'Hancock', 2008, 'images/8960 poster.jpg', 6.1, 'images/8960 cover.jpg', 'Hancock is a down-and-out superhero who''s forced to employ a PR expert to help repair his image when the public grows weary of all the damage he''s inflicted during his lifesaving heroics. The agent''s idea of imprisoning the antihero to make the world miss him proves successful, but will Hancock stick to his new sense of purpose or slip back into old habits?', 'en', '2008-07-01', 'Peter Berg', 'Columbia Pictures', '92 minutes', '150000000', '624029371', 8, ' ', 'Bad Behavior. Bad Attitude. Real Hero.', '2008-07-01 00:00:00'),
(515, '98', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0172495', 'Gladiator', 2000, 'images/98 poster.jpg', 7.8, 'images/98 cover.jpg', 'In the year 180, the death of emperor Marcus Aurelius throws the Roman Empire into chaos. Maximus is one of the Roman army''s most capable and trusted generals and a key advisor to the emperor. As Marcus'' devious son Commodus ascends to the throne, Maximus is set to be executed. He escapes, but is captured by slave traders. Renamed Spaniard and forced to become a gladiator, Maximus must battle to the death with other men for the amusement of paying audiences. His battle skills serve him well, and he becomes one of the most famous and admired men to fight in the Colosseum. Determined to avenge himself against the man who took away his freedom and laid waste to his family, Maximus believes that he can use his fame and skill in the ring to avenge the loss of his family and former glory. As the gladiator begins to challenge his rule, Commodus decides to put his own fighting mettle to the test by squaring off with Maximus in a battle to the death.', 'en', '2000-05-01', 'Ridley Scott', 'DreamWorks SKG', '155 minutes', '103000000', '457640427', 6, ' ', 'A Hero Will Rise.', '2000-05-01 00:00:00'),
(516, '497', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120689', 'The Green Mile', 1999, 'images/497 poster.jpg', 8.2, 'images/497 cover.jpg', 'A supernatural tale set on death row in a Southern prison, where gentle giant John Coffey possesses the mysterious power to heal people''s ailments. When the cellblock''s head guard, Paul Edgecomb, recognizes Coffey''s miraculous gift, he tries desperately to help stave off the condemned man''s execution.', 'en', '1999-12-10', 'Frank Darabont', 'Castle Rock Entertainment', '189 minutes', '60000000', '284600000', 7, ' ', 'Miracles do happen.', '1999-12-10 00:00:00'),
(517, '321612', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2771200', 'Beauty and the Beast', 2017, 'images/321612 poster.jpg', 6.8, 'images/321612 cover.jpg', 'A live-action adaptation of Disney''s version of the classic ''Beauty and the Beast'' tale of a cursed prince and a beautiful young woman who helps him break the spell.', 'en', '2017-03-16', 'Bill Condon', 'Walt Disney Pictures', '129 minutes', '160000000', '1256977550', 6, '', 'Be our guest.', '2017-07-13 01:28:15'),
