(617, '51999', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1439572', 'Perfect Sense', 2011, 'images/51999 poster.jpg', 6.8, 'images/51999 cover.jpg', 'Susan is a scientist searching for answers to important questions. So important that she has given up on other things, like love - until she meets Micheal. Susan and Michael find themselves embarking on a sensual adventure while the world around them seems to be falling apart. A life-affirming look at what it means to love and be loved in turbulent times.', 'en', '2011-01-24', 'David Mackenzie', 'Zentropa Entertainments', '92 minutes', 'unknown', '908000', 6, '', 'Without love there is nothing.', '2017-07-18 19:05:57'),
(618, '752', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0434409', 'V for Vendetta', 2006, 'images/752 poster.jpg', 7.7, 'images/752 cover.jpg', 'In a world in which Great Britain has become a fascist state, a masked vigilante known only as ''V'' conducts guerrilla warfare against the oppressive British government. When ''V'' rescues a young woman from the secret police, he finds in her an ally with whom he can continue his fight to free the people of Britain.', 'en', '2006-03-15', 'James McTeigue', 'Studio Babelsberg', '132 minutes', '54000000', '132511035', 7, ' ', 'People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.', '2006-03-15 00:00:00'),
(619, '20916', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0306855', 'Style', 2001, 'images/20916 poster.jpg', 6, 'images/20916 cover.jpg', 'Style is a 2001 Bollywood low-budget film mostly regarded as a forgettable romantic-comedy caper by critics. Even though the movie was greatly criticized, it was a commercial success.', 'hi', '2001-12-28', 'N. Chandra', 'N Chandra Global Infotainment Ltd', '159 minutes', 'unknown', 'unknown', 7, ' ', '', '2001-12-28 00:00:00'),
(620, '277547', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2139555', 'Playing It Cool', 2014, 'images/277547 poster.jpg', 5.6, 'images/277547 cover.jpg', 'The story of a young man disillusioned by love who meets a breathtaking young woman at a charity dinner by pretending to be a philanthropist. Turns out that sheâ€™s engaged to a guy who doesnâ€™t like her going on dates. Challenged by the chase, and egged on by his eclectic friends, he feigns a platonic relationship in order to keep seeing her as he tries to conquer her heart', 'en', '2014-09-26', 'Justin Reardon', 'Wonderland Sound and Vision', '94 minutes', 'unknown', 'unknown', 6, '', 'Love... it''s a balancing act', '2017-07-19 23:27:27'),
(621, '3638', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0481141', 'No Reservations', 2007, 'images/3638 poster.jpg', 6, 'images/3638 cover.jpg', 'Master chef Kate Armstrong runs her life and her kitchen with intimidating intensity. However, a recipe for disaster may be in the works when she becomes the guardian of her young niece while crossing forks with the brash sous-chef who just joined her staff. Though romance blooms in the face of rivalry, Kate needs to look outside the kitchen to find true happiness.', 'en', '2007-07-25', 'Scott Hicks', 'Village Roadshow Pictures', '104 minutes', '28000000', '92601050', 6, '', 'Life isn''t always made to order.', '2017-07-19 23:35:03'),
(622, '84355', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1742336', 'Your Sister''s Sister', 2011, 'images/84355 poster.jpg', 6.5, 'images/84355 cover.jpg', 'Iris invites her friend Jack to stay at her family''s island getaway after the death of his brother. At their remote cabin, Jack''s drunken encounter with Hannah, Iris'' sister, kicks off a revealing stretch of days.', 'en', '2011-09-11', 'Lynn Shelton', 'Ada Films', '90 minutes', '125000', '3200000', 6, '', 'A comedy about doing the right thing with the wrong person.', '2017-07-19 23:35:25'),
(623, '325346', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3714720', 'The Hollars', 2016, 'images/325346 poster.jpg', 6.4, 'images/325346 cover.jpg', 'Aspiring New York City artist, John Hollar returns to his Middle America hometown on the eve of his motherâ€™s brain surgery. Joined by his girlfriend, eight months pregnant with their first child, John is forced to navigate the crazy world he left behind.', 'en', '2016-08-25', 'John Krasinski', 'Groundswell Productions', '105 minutes', 'unknown', 'unknown', 6, '', '', '2017-07-19 23:55:52'),
(624, '616', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0325710', 'The Last Samurai', 2003, 'images/616 poster.jpg', 7.2, 'images/616 cover.jpg', 'Nathan Algren is an American hired to instruct the Japanese army in the ways of modern warfare, which finds him learning to respect the samurai and the honorable principles that rule them. Pressed to destroy the samurai''s way of life in the name of modernization and open trade, Algren decides to become an ultimate warrior himself and to fight for their right to exist.', 'en', '2003-12-05', 'Edward Zwick', 'Cruise/Wagner Productions', '154 minutes', '140000000', '456758981', 7, '', 'In the face of an enemy, in the heart of one man, lies the soul of a warrior.', '2017-07-20 02:59:59'),
