(628, '9470', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0373074', 'Kung Fu Hustle', 2004, 'images/9470 poster.jpg', 7.2, 'images/9470 cover.jpg', 'Set in Canton, China in the 1940s, the story revolves in a town ruled by the Axe Gang, Sing who desperately wants to become a member. He stumbles into a slum ruled by eccentric landlords who turns out to be the greatest kung-fu masters in disguise. Sing''s actions eventually cause the Axe Gang and the slumlords to engage in an explosive kung-fu battle. Only one side will win and only one hero will emerge as the greatest kung-fu master of all.', 'cn', '2004-09-14', 'Stephen Chow', 'Columbia Pictures', '99 minutes', '20000000', '100914445', 7, ' ', 'So many gangsters...so little time.', '2004-09-14 00:00:00'),
