(650, '185008', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2178470', 'Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani', 2013, 'images/185008 poster.jpg', 7.2, 'images/185008 cover.jpg', 'Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani features two polar opposite characters, who at one point were classmates in Modern School. The first is Naina Talwar (Deepika Padukone), a studious bespectacled young girl. The second is Bunny (Ranbir Kapoor), a carefree young travel-show host, intent on breaking out of the pattern of getting an education, a career, a wife, children, retirement, and eventually death.', 'hi', '2013-05-31', 'Ayan Mukherjee', 'Dharma Productions', '159 minutes', '7700000', '46000000', 6, ' ', '', '2013-05-31 00:00:00'),
