(652, '371741', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt4072326', 'Ali and Nino', 2016, 'images/371741 poster.jpg', 7.3, 'images/371741 cover.jpg', 'Muslim prince Ali and Georgian aristocrat Nino have grown up in the Russian province of Azerbaijan. Their tragic love story sees the outbreak of the First World War and the worldâ€™s struggle for Bakuâ€™s oil. Ultimately they must choose to fight for their countryâ€™s independence or for each other.', 'en', '2016-01-27', 'Asif Kapadia', 'PeaPie Films', '100 minutes', 'unknown', 'unknown', 5, ' ', '', '2017-08-01 23:53:15'),
