(662, '11003', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120888', 'The Wedding Singer', 1998, 'images/11003 poster.jpg', 6.5, 'images/11003 cover.jpg', 'Robbie, a local rock star turned wedding singer, is dumped on the day of his wedding. Meanwhile, waitress Julia finally sets a wedding date with her fiancÃ©e Glenn. When Julia and Robbie meet and hit it off, they find that things are more complicated than anybody thought.', 'en', '1998-02-13', 'Frank Coraci', 'New Line Cinema', '95 minutes', '18000000', '123306987', 6, '', 'He''s gonna party like it''s 1985.', '2017-08-02 02:11:59'),
(663, '203321', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1808339', 'Not Another Happy Ending', 2013, 'images/203321 poster.jpg', 6, 'images/203321 cover.jpg', 'When a struggling publisher discovers his only successful author is blocked he knows he has to unblock her or he''s finished. With her newfound success, she''s become too damn happy and she can''t write when she''s happy.The only trouble is, the worse he makes her feel, the more he realises he''s in love with her.', 'en', '2013-10-11', 'John McKay', 'Synchronicity Films', '102 minutes', 'unknown', 'unknown', 6, '', 'Sometimes love needs a re-write.', '2017-08-02 12:58:04'),
