(682, '2642', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0313737', 'Two Weeks Notice', 2002, 'images/2642 poster.jpg', 5.9, 'images/2642 cover.jpg', 'Dedicated environmental lawyer Lucy Kelson goes to work for billionaire George Wade as part of a deal to preserve a community center. Indecisive and weak-willed George grows dependent on Lucy''s guidance on everything from legal matters to clothing. Exasperated, Lucy gives notice and picks Harvard graduate June Carter as her replacement. As Lucy''s time at the firm nears an end, she grows jealous of June and has second thoughts about leaving George.', 'en', '2002-12-19', 'Marc Lawrence', 'Village Roadshow Pictures', '101 minutes', '60000000', '93354918', 6, '', 'Over. Done. Finished. A comedy about love at last glance.', '2017-08-12 01:34:38'),
