(702, '118628', 'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2181931', 'English Vinglish', 2012, 'images/118628 poster.jpg', 7.2, 'images/118628 cover.jpg', 'English Vinglish is the story of a woman who does not know English and is made to feel insecure by her family and society at large.Circumstances make her determined to overcome this insecurity, master the language, and teach the world a lesson on the way to becoming a self assured and confident woman.', 'hi', '2012-09-14', 'Gauri Shinde', 'Eros International', '133 minutes', '2840000', '11620000', 7, '', 'Sridevi vs Angrezi', '2012-09-14 00:00:00'),
