(256, 9, 'LCD Soundsystem', '2015-11-04', 'Gretchen becomes fascinated by a slightly older, cool couple that appears to have it all. Jimmy employs a punishment-based system to ensure he meets his writing deadline.'),
(256, 10, 'A Right Proper Story', '2015-11-11', 'Jimmyâ€™s trashy family comes to visit from England, much to Jimmyâ€™s dismay. In the throes of her depression, Gretchen struggles to help Jimmy entertain them. Lindsay fills in for Gretchen at work. Edgar bonds with Jimmyâ€™s little sister.'),
(256, 11, 'A Rapidly Mutating Virus', '2015-11-18', 'Jimmy gets closer to his bartender friend, Nina. Gretchen accompanies Sam to do a radio interview. Edgar attempts to make inroads with Dorothy''s comedy friends.'),
(256, 12, 'Other Things You Could Be Doing', '2015-12-02', 'Gretchenâ€™s depression comes to a head, forcing Jimmy to make a tough choice. Lindsay finally lets Paul go. Edgar has his improv graduation show.'),
