(287, 9, 'Uninvited Guests', '2015-08-19', 'Rachel and her mother, Laura Zane, plan for Rachel''s dream wedding, but Rachel fears the event may reveal Mike''s secret. Meanwhile Daniel Hardman and Jack Soloff make their move against Jessica and the partners, as Harvey and Mike tangle with Hardman''s mysterious backer, and Louis tries to find Jack''s Achilles heel.'),
