(325, 8, 'Episode 8', '2017-02-25', 'As James Delaney conspires to escape, an enraged Prince Regent unleashes one final plan to destroy him.'),
(326, 1, 'Pilot', '2008-09-23', 'CBI consultant Patrick Jane, Senior Agent Teresa Lisbon and her team investigate the double murder in Palm Springs of a pro golfer''s wife and her doctor, which has the hallmarks of a serial killer with a personal connection to Jane.'),
(326, 2, 'Red Hair and Silver Tape', '2008-09-30', 'While Lisbon and her team investigate the murder of a young waitress in the Napa Valley, Jane goes behind Lisbon''s back to orchestrate his own undercover operation using Van Pelt as bait.'),
(326, 3, 'Red Tide', '2008-10-14', 'When a high school girl''s body washes up on the beach, Patrick Jane sets a mentalist trap in order to get her surfing friends to turn on each other and reveal what really happened.'),
(326, 4, 'Ladies in Red', '2008-10-21', 'When the team learns that a wealthy investment banker found murdered inside his locked safe room was living a dual life and skimming millions from clients, Patrick Jane sets up a mental conundrum to see which of the suspects will show their true colors.'),
(326, 5, 'Redwood', '2008-10-28', 'When a girl is found covered in blood and holding the murder weapon that killed her best friend, she becomes an obvious suspect, though she can''t remember anything. But Jane, believing she''s innocent, engineers a risky maneuver in which she must relive the terrifying events in order to spark her memory.'),
(326, 6, 'Red Handed', '2008-11-11', 'While investigating the case of a murdered casino owner, Patrick Jane uses his mentalist skills to ultimately entrap the killer, and win big at the card tables.\n\n'),
(326, 7, 'Seeing Red', '2008-11-18', 'Patrick Jane goes head-to-head with a ''psychic'' he suspects of murder. Intent on proving the so-called psychic is a fraud -- as well as a killer -- Jane arranges a sÃ©ance to expose the murderer.'),
(326, 8, 'The Thin Red Line', '2008-11-25', 'While the police suspect a drug dealer on trial is behind the murders of the State''s witness in his case, as well as his girlfriend, Patrick Jane sees a different motive for the crime -- as well as a different suspect.'),
(326, 9, 'Flame Red', '2008-12-02', 'Patrick Jane suspects the only surviving member of a National Guard unit of murdering his friends - and goes undercover to prove it.'),
(326, 10, 'Red Brick and Ivy', '2008-12-16', 'When a leading scientific researcher is killed by poisoning, Patrick Jane takes a personal interest in the case when he learns the prime suspect is the victim''s wife - and Jane''s former psychiatrist.'),
(326, 11, 'Red John''s Friends', '2009-01-06', 'Enticed by the promise from a convicted murder that he''ll reveal information about Red John upon his release, Patrick Jane becomes singularly focused and quits the CBI in order to prove the prisoner is innocent.'),
(326, 12, 'Red Rum', '2009-01-13', 'Patrick Jane sets a mentalist trap to find out who is responsible for the murder of a high school boy who antagonized the local self-proclaimed witch by killing her cat.'),
(326, 13, 'Paint It Red', '2009-01-18', 'While it appears obvious that a business tycoon''s son-in-law was in on the robbery of a $50 million painting since his body is found where the painting once hung, Patrick Jane suspects others, including a Russian oil baron, an art forger and an art curator.'),
(326, 14, 'Crimson Casanova', '2009-02-10', 'With Patrick Jane''s help, Cho goes undercover as a sweet-talking ladies man with all the right moves in order to catch a pick-up artist and killer with his own set of pseudo-mentalist techniques.'),
(326, 15, 'Scarlett Fever', '2009-02-17', 'As Jane and the team investigate the poisoning death of the ''queen bee'' in a country club, they discover that the community is full of secrets, including love affairs and drug abuse'),
(326, 16, 'Bloodshot', '2009-03-17', 'Patrick Jane must rely on his other senses during the murder investigation of a financial advisor when he loses his sight as a result of an explosion.'),
(326, 17, 'Carnelian Inc.', '2009-03-24', 'A story of greed and betrayal pits Patrick Jane against a group of financiers when the CBI investigates a series of murders at a corporate retreat in the wilds of the Sierra Nevada foothills.'),
(326, 18, 'Russet Potatoes', '2009-03-31', 'Patrick Jane and the CBI team track down a mastermind who hypnotizes people into doing their bidding.'),
(326, 19, 'A Dozen Red Roses', '2009-04-07', 'Patrick Jane and the team go to Hollywood when they investigate the murder of a movie producer.'),
(326, 20, 'Red Sauce', '2009-04-28', 'Patrick Jane and the CBI team investigate the murder of a mobster who was in the witness protection program.'),
(326, 21, 'Miss Red', '2009-05-05', 'Patrick Jane uses his mentalist skills to play suspects off each other in order to solve the case of a wealthy software company CEO found murdered on his yacht.'),
(326, 22, 'Blood Brothers', '2009-05-12', 'Patrick Jane must find a clever way to convince the troubled kids in a wilderness program to confide in him about what really happened surrounding the death of one of their peers.'),
(326, 23, 'Red John''s Footsteps', '2009-05-19', 'Lisbon fears that the serial killer Red John is drawing Patrick Jane into a trap when the CBI team investigates the murder of a young girl and the abduction of her twin sister.'),
(327, 1, 'Redemption', '2009-09-24', 'Jane and Lisbon learn that the Red John case has been reassigned to a different CBI team led by the straight-shooting officer Sam Bosco.'),
(327, 2, 'The Scarlet Letter', '2009-10-01', 'Lisbon and the team work the case of a State Senator''s murdered intern, while Jane simultaneously tries to find out what new information Bosco has uncovered on the Red John case.'),
(327, 3, 'Red Badge', '2009-10-08', 'Jane, Cho, Rigsby and Van Pelt decide to conduct their own investigation when Lisbon is accused of murdering a child molester she arrested who was recently paroled.'),
(327, 4, 'Red Menace', '2009-10-15', 'Jane and the CBI investigate the murder of Gordon Hodge, a powerful attorney, who is responsible for allowing a vicious murderer, Van McBride, to walk away a free man.'),
(327, 5, 'Red Scare', '2009-10-29', 'Jane and the CBI team are called in to investigate the death of a prominent architect found murdered in a crumbling old mansion, and there appears to be a number of suspects.'),
(327, 6, 'Black Gold and Red Blood', '2009-11-05', 'Even after Bosco arrests Jane and puts him in prison for spying on him, Jane is able to help the CBI team from his cell to solve the murder of a young man.'),
(327, 7, 'Red Bulls', '2009-11-12', 'Minelli orders Patrick Jane and Lisbon and company to play nice and work together with Bosco and his team to locate a kidnapped woman being held for ransom.'),
(327, 8, 'His Red Right Hand', '2009-11-19', 'The CBI team is faced with a violent and shocking crime in their own office, but must work the case in spite of their alarm of who may be behind it. Meanwhile, Rigsby and Van Pelt are definitely an ''item''.'),
(327, 9, 'A Price Above Rubies', '2009-12-10', 'Patrick Jane and the team are called to investigate the robbery and murder of a wealthy jeweler while attending a black tie fundraiser for the CBI.'),
(327, 10, 'Throwing Fire', '2009-12-17', 'While Jane and the team examine the crime scene where a baseball scout is found murdered, Jane is clocked in the head by a ball and flashes back to his childhood with his overbearing father.'),
(327, 11, 'Rose-Colored Glasses', '2010-01-14', 'Jane and company investigate the murder of a man and his wife, on her way to his fifteen year high school reunion where, clearly, the attendees haven''t changed all that much.'),
(327, 12, 'Bleeding Heart', '2010-01-21', 'Patrick Jane and the team investigate the murder of a mayor''s aide, and Rigsby and Van Pelt make a big announcement.'),
(327, 13, 'Redline', '2010-02-04', 'Patrick Jane and the CBI team investigate when the body of a high-end luxury car sales woman is found in the trunk of a Bentley in the dealership''s showroom.'),
(327, 14, 'Blood In, Blood Out', '2010-02-11', 'When a member of Cho''s former gang, the Avon Park Playboys, is found murdered, Patrick Jane insists on helping Cho with his off-the-books investigation.'),
(327, 15, 'Red Herring', '2010-03-04', 'Jane and the team investigate the murder of an arrogant chef during a cooking competition in Napa Valley.'),
(327, 16, 'Code Red', '2010-03-11', 'When Dr. Alicia Seberg, a government research scientist, is exposed to a deadly toxin while at work and has only hours to live, she calls Patrick Jane and the CBI to find her murderer.'),
(327, 17, 'The Red Box', '2010-04-01', 'Patrick and the CBI team investigate the murder of a tutor, and find a mysterious little red box near the body, starting a chain of events that turns the murder into the search for a priceless ring stolen from the British Museum. Meanwhile, Lisbon is worried when a new boss, Madeleine Hightower, takes command of the CBI, as well as mysteriously learning about Rigsby and Van Pelt''s relationship.'),
(327, 18, 'Aingavite Baa', '2010-04-08', 'When a ''Jane Doe'' with amnesia and covered in blood steps in front of Cho and Van Pelt''s car, Patrick Jane must use all of his skills to discover who she is, her last location and why she lost her memory'),
(327, 19, 'Blood Money', '2010-04-22', 'When Patrick Jane''s sneaky conduct causes the case of a confessed hitman to be tossed out of court, his annoyed CBI team must start the investigation over from scratch.'),
(327, 20, 'Red All Over', '2010-04-29', 'When a media mogul is murdered, Patrick Jane and the CBI team investigate cult leader Bret Stiles, who may have had an axe to grind following the publication of a critical story about his group.'),
(327, 21, '18-5-4', '2010-05-06', 'Patrick Jane and the CBI team investigate the death of a mathematical genius by a gun-wielding clown.'),
(327, 22, 'Red Letter', '2010-05-13', 'Romantic sparks begin to fly when Patrick Jane and supposed psychic Kristina Frye cross paths again during the CBI investigation into the murder of a charismatic head of a non-profit organization that fights human trafficking.'),
(327, 23, 'Red Sky in the Morning', '2010-05-20', 'Patrick Jane and Kristina''s first date is interrupted by a report of Red John striking again, which is discovered to be a copycat. But when Kristina reaches out to the real Red John, both she and Jane find themselves in grave danger.'),
(328, 1, 'Friends and Enemies', '2014-01-19', 'Young swordsman d''Artagnan arrives in Paris seeking the man responsible for killing his father â€“ a quest that brings him into conflict with one of the king''s guards. But as he quickly discovers, when you take on one Musketeer, you take on them all. It''s soon back to business when the swashbuckling heroes are ordered to find a missing soldier who was carrying important letters on behalf of King Louis, while the dastardly Cardinal Richelieu plots to increase his political power.'),
(328, 2, 'Sleight of Hand', '2014-01-26', 'Notorious criminal Vadim seeks to make life unbearable for the authorities that have imprisoned him. When he engineers a full-scale riot, it falls to the Musketeers to protect those whom he seeks to destroy.'),
(328, 3, 'Commodities', '2014-02-02', 'The Musketeers must escort a merchant trader back to Paris and thwart his enemies.'),
(328, 4, 'The Good Soldier', '2014-02-09', 'Aramis helps an old friend to uncover the truth behind a disastrous mission.'),
(328, 5, 'The Homecoming', '2014-02-23', 'Porthos wakes up after his drunken birthday celebrations with a dead body next to him. The Musketeers must prove his innocence as he gets sentenced to death.'),
(328, 6, 'The Exiles', '2014-03-02', 'Aramis and the other Musketeers help a young mother rescue her abducted baby son.'),
(328, 7, 'A Rebellious Woman', '2014-03-09', 'The musketeers help save an enlightened woman who has been accused of witchcraft.'),
(328, 8, 'The Challenge', '2014-03-16', 'A contest between the Musketeers and Red Guards gives D''Artagnan a chance to prove himself.'),
(328, 9, 'Knight Takes Queen', '2014-03-23', 'The Musketeers come under siege in a convent whilst protecting the queen''s life.'),
(328, 10, 'Musketeers Don''t Die Easily', '2014-03-30', 'Milady seeks her revenge against the Musketeers. Will the Musketeers outwit her or will she destroy them by manipulating their weakest link, D''Artagnan?'),
(329, 1, 'Keep Your Friends Close', '2015-01-02', 'The Musketeers must rescue a French general from an impenetrable Spanish prison.'),
(329, 2, 'An Ordinary Man', '2015-01-09', 'D''Artagnan must protect King Louis when a notorious criminal kidnaps them both.'),
(329, 3, 'The Good Traitor', '2015-01-16', 'The Musketeers help rescue an enemy''s daughter in exchange for a deadly gunpowder formula.'),
(329, 4, 'Emilie', '2015-01-30', 'A woman claims to have visions from God which instruct her to start a war with Spain.'),
(329, 5, 'The Return', '2015-02-13', 'Athos must confront his past to protect the people he left behind.'),
(329, 6, 'Through a Glass Darkly', '2015-02-20', 'An astronomer gathers the royal party to see an eclipse, but events take a dramatic turn.'),
(329, 7, 'A Marriage of Inconvenience', '2015-02-27', 'The Kingâ€™s cousin is ambushed while under Musketeer escort as she travels from Mantua to Sweden to make a political marriage that will be advantageous to France.'),
(329, 8, 'The Prodigal Father', '2015-03-06', 'Porthos uncovers the truth about his past and questions his allegiance to the Musketeers.'),
(329, 9, 'The Accused', '2015-03-20', 'The Musketeers must put their lives on the line when the queen is accused of treason.'),
(329, 10, 'Trial and Punishment', '2015-03-27', 'The Musketeers must risk everything to save France from Rochefort''s treacherous plan.'),
(330, 1, 'Spoils of War', '2016-05-28', 'Athos, Porthos and D''Artagnan are fighting on the battlefront while Aramis has trouble living in contemplation as a monk. The Musketeers'' search for missing gunpowder lead them to follow bandits to Aramis'' monastery, where circumstance force them to collaborate to save the monastery''s children and brothers. Aramis'' finally accepts his true calling as a Musketeer and rejoins his brothers-in-arms in Paris.'),
(330, 2, 'The Hunger', '2016-06-04', 'The corrupt Governor of Paris conspires with the Duke de Beaufort, primary provider of food for Paris, to stage a robbery of the city''s granary and pin it on the refugees, only to later sell the stolen grain back to the King at an inflated price. D''Artagnan is taken captive along with the rioting refugees, and the other Musketeers (along with D''Artagnan''s wife Constance, now in charge of the Musketeer garrison) must rescue them from the hands of the Red Guard before they are executed.'),
(330, 3, 'Brother in Arms', '2016-06-11', 'King Louis tasks the Musketeers with bringing his exiled brother, the Duke of OrlÃ©ans, back to Paris in order to mend bridges. On the way, the Duke is robbed of dangerous letters which could destroy OrlÃ©ans. The Duke informs the corrupt Governor of this, and the Governor''s Red Guard must race the Musketeers in the hunt for the thief.'),
(330, 4, 'The Queen''s Diamonds', '2016-06-18', 'Bonnaire is back, and the Musketeers need him to save the future of the English Crown.'),
(330, 5, 'To Play the King', '2016-06-25', 'The Musketeers battle to restore order in Paris after Grimaud and Feron stage an ambitious ChÃ¢telet breakout, setting free a lunatic with murderous designs on the Louvre.'),
(330, 6, 'Death of a Hero', '2016-07-02', 'It''s the day of reckoning, as Grimaud vows to kill the Musketeers in a series of savage co-ordinated attacks and puts Feron to the ultimate test in his bid for power. The furious battle for survival sparks a series of revelations that threaten to destroy Paris. Before the day is out, a hero falls, thereâ€™s a traitor on the rise and the Musketeers will be changed forever.'),
(330, 7, 'Fool''s Gold', '2016-07-09', 'Chasing Grimaud, the Musketeers make a troubling discovery in a village ruled by women.'),
(330, 8, 'Prisoners of War', '2016-07-16', 'The Queen''s reputation is on the line after Grimaud kidnaps Aramis.'),
(330, 9, 'The Prize', '2016-07-23', 'When death strikes the Louvre, Treville takes controversial steps to protect the Dauphin from the unholy alliance of Grimaud, Gaston and the Duke of Lorraine. His secretive tactics isolate the Queen and threaten to drive even his loyal Musketeers apart.'),
(330, 10, 'We Are the Garrison', '2016-07-30', ''),
(331, 1, 'Episode 1', '2016-02-21', 'Hotel night manager Jonathan Pine receives a plea for help from a well-connected guest.'),
(331, 2, 'Episode 2', '2016-02-28', 'On the Mediterranean island of Mallorca, Roperâ€™s life of luxury and calm is shattered. Six months earlier, Burr continues her recruitment of Pine, sending him to Devon to build his cover story.'),
(331, 3, 'Episode 3', '2016-03-06', 'While he continues to recuperate in Roperâ€™s villa, Pine starts to dig up secrets about the other members of the household. Meanwhile, Burr and Steadman seize on an opportunity to recruit a new asset.'),
(331, 4, 'Episode 4', '2016-03-13', 'Roper welcomes Pine into his inner circle, leaving Corky out in the cold. Meanwhile, Burr has concerns for the safety of her source, when she suspects key information has been leaked to the River House.'),
(331, 5, 'Episode 5', '2016-03-20', 'A suspicious Roper gathers his entourage around him in an attempt to root out the traitor, forcing Pine to play a dangerous game. In London, Burr and Steadman face mounting opposition from Whitehall.'),
(331, 6, 'Episode 6', '2016-03-27', 'Roper and his team return to Cairo for the deal, reuniting Pine with an old enemy. Pine risks it all to put his plan in motion. A discredited Burr makes one last stand.'),
(332, 1, 'Stand and Unfold Yourself', '2015-03-15', 'After the sudden death of their older brother and heir to the throne, Prince Liam and Princess Eleanor have a hard time with their new roles. Queen Helena tries to maintain the family''s image and King Simon questions the monarchy''s future.'),
(332, 2, 'Infants of the Spring', '2015-03-22', 'At the annual garden party, Prince Liam is reunited with his ex, Gemma. The Queen and Cyrus work to counteract King Simon''s wishes.'),
(332, 3, 'We Are Pictures, or Mere Beasts', '2015-03-29', 'The Queen and Princess Eleanor throw competing fashion shows during London''s fashion week while Prince Liam narrowly avoids a catastrophe.'),
(332, 4, 'Sweet, Not Lasting', '2015-04-05', 'Prince Liam does his first PR tour as heir to the throne while Queen Helena forces Princess Eleanor to do a PR tour of London.'),
(332, 5, 'Unmask Her Beauty to the Moon', '2015-04-12', 'Prince Liam, Princess Eleanor and Queen Helena''s romances are a popular topic at the annual masquerade ball.'),
(332, 6, 'The Slings and Arrows of Outrageous Fortune', '2015-04-19', 'A trip to Monaco helps Prince Liam and Ophelia''s relationship blossom but a different side of Princess Eleanor is revealed.'),
(332, 7, 'Your Sovereignty of Reason', '2015-04-26', 'The King makes a decision that impacts the rest of the family while Ophelia struggles with the PR fallout from Monaco.'),
(332, 8, 'The Great Man Down', '2015-05-03', 'The Royal Family is put on lockdown in a safe room at the palace after an assassination attempt.'),
(332, 9, 'In My Heart There Was a Kind of Fighting', '2015-05-10', 'When someone from Prince Robert''s past pays them a visit, Prince Liam and Princess Eleanor must face their own personal demons.'),
(332, 10, 'Our Wills and Fates Do So Contrary Run', '2015-05-17', 'Secrets are revealed as Prince Liam and Princess Eleanor investigate Prince Robertâ€™s death and the attack on the throne.'),
(333, 1, 'It Is Not, nor It Cannot Come to Good', '2015-11-15', 'In the wake of King Simonâ€™s death, King Cyrusâ€™ new look monarchy is on full display at the Royal polo match, Prince Liam is hell-bent on revenge and receives some unexpected help, and Queen Helena maneuvers for power.'),
(333, 2, 'Welcome Is Fashion and Ceremony', '2015-11-22', 'In Prince Liam''s quest for vengeance, a secret is revealed that affects the monarchy''s future while Princess Eleanor rekindles an old flame.'),
(333, 3, 'Is Not This Something More Than Fantasy?', '2015-11-29', 'Prince Liam and Princess Eleanor both take trips that donâ€™t end as they expected, while at home Queen Helena meets a new rival and King Cyrus receives some bad news.'),
(333, 4, 'What, Has This Thing Appear''d Again Tonight?', '2015-12-06', 'King Cyrus draws a line in the sand with Queen Helena and Prince Liam as he does whatever he can to eliminate King Simonâ€™s legacy. Princess Eleanor makes a friend as a new wrinkle in the Kingâ€™s murder is potentially revealed.'),
(333, 5, 'The Spirit That I Have Seen', '2015-12-13', 'Princess Eleanorâ€™s new relationship makes waves in and outside of the palace as King Cyrus uses a public ceremony to solidify his image and Queen Helena learns of betrayal.'),
(333, 6, 'Doubt Truth to Be a Liar', '2015-12-20', 'The twins have a birthday party in the palace and things get out of hand. Queen Helena and Prince Liam look to the past for answers about the future.'),
(333, 7, 'Taint Not Thy Mind, nor Let Thy Soul Contrive Against Thy Mother', '2015-12-27', 'Queen Helena and Princess Eleanor share some unexpected bonding time as Prince Liam investigates Domino.'),
